Content.Text:
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Good morning, <PARENT>. Now that I'm
bigger my bed is a bit too small.
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>I'm worried I might break it! Not
because I'm too heavy, before you say
anything!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Good morning, <PARENT>. I'm a little
relieved to find out I'm going to be
beautiful when I finish growing up.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Good morning, <PARENT>. I'm starting to
think maybe I should diet a little...
I never needed to when I was smaller.
<PAGE>
I ate so much back then, wanting to get
bigger, but now I'm just worried about
getting fat!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>, <PARENT>. I want to put on some
make up, but could you show me how?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>, shall we play house? I'm sure
it will still be a lot of fun!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, <PARENT>. Now that I'm bigger I
can reach higher places. It's fun
growing up, isn't it?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, <PARENT>. Is it true that not
getting enough sleep is bad for your
skin?
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>Then I'd better get to bed quickly!
Good night!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Good night, <PARENT>. Good luck with your
work again tomorrow!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, welcome home! Take it easy after
another long day at work, okay?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, what fantastic weather! A great
day for working hard.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I want to avoid getting my hair wet
today. It takes so long to dry it out!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Sunlight in summer is bad for you?
Really? Better not to get too tanned,
then. I'll be careful.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I like summertime rain. It's better
getting wet by a little rain than it is
being drenched in sweat.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
The food is so good in fall! Just got
to be careful not to eat too much.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
I hate the rain! It's ruining my hair.
This is the worst!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<PARENT>, have winters always been this
cold? My feet are freezing! It wasn't
like this when I was small.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
The snow has turned the house into a
refrigerator! <PARENT>, can't you do
something? Please!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Yikes! The window is going to rattle
right out of the frame!
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY><PARENT>, don't leave me alone! I'm too
scared!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
It's snowing so heavily out there. Looks
like we'll be snowed in tomorrow.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
There's this shortcut I used when I was
smaller, but now I'm too big to use it.
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>H-Hey! It's not because I've got fat,
okay? I'm just bigger now!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Now that I'm bigger I can see places
higher up.
<PAGE>
Being taller means I can make all sorts
of new discoveries in places higher up.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Eating something out here is a great
way to make small animals gather. Always
looking for a free meal!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I've collected lots of things to eat.
Now I just have to get them home...

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
It's fine having these long legs now,
but it's taking a little getting used
to...

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Maybe I'll put on a swimsuit and swim
in the lake... I hope that strange
lady doesn't get angry again!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Now that I'm bigger I finally understand
some of the things you go through,
<PARENT>. Let me know if I can help you!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
It's a lot of fun helping you out,
<PARENT>. I'm loving life on the farm
even more each day!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I was really scared of this mine when
I was smaller... and I'm still a little
scared of it now.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, have you found the ore you
were looking for? I hope you find lots
of it!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, why aren't there more people
here in town? I wish there were more
people to play with!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Who should I play with today? Who do
you think, <PARENT>? You can come along
too, <PARENT>!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Who should I play with today? Who do
you think, <PARENT>? You can come along
too, <PARENT>!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Who should I play with today? Who do
you think, <PARENT>? You can come along
too, <PARENT>!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I'm happy that I've got bigger, but
there are some problems with it too.
<PAGE>
I keep bumping my head. At least once
a day! Owwwie!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I thought I'd try learning something a
little more feminine, some sewing, but I
was so bad at it. It was so hard!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I'm helping with cooking. It's quite a
lot of fun. Maybe I've found my calling?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
When my friends saw me looking like this
they all said they wanted some adult
candy of their own!
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>What? They can't? They aren't going to
be happy to hear that.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
When I'm walking through town guys often
give me things. It's pretty great being
grown up!
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>W-What's that? You want to know who's
giving them to me? Why... why are you so
angry?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
When the effects of the candy wears off
I'll become small again, right?
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>Hummm, I'm not sure I want to turn back.
I wonder when it's going to happen...

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
You're something else, <PARENT>. After
getting big myself, I've got a feeling
for how hard work truly is.
<PAGE>
Thank you so much for always working so
hard for me, <PARENT>.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>'s pancakes! No matter how big I
get, I'll always love these. Yum!
They're so tasty!
<PAGE>
Next time, I'll try making pancakes
myself. Now that I'm bigger, I should be
able to do it, right?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A present for me? Wow! <PARENT>, thank
you!
<PAGE>
Time to dig in! Oh, delicious! I just
better be careful not to eat too much.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Yay! A present! Even though I'm an adult
now, getting presents still makes me
happy.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Even though I'm an adult, I still don't
don't like this one bit.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
What's wrong with you, <PARENT>?! I didn't
get bigger just so you could torture me
like this!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Grilled pumpkin?! I thought I might be
able to eat this now that I'm an adult,
but I still can't stand it.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Wow... that's a big watermelon! Thanks,
<PARENT>! Let's all eat it together.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Wow! I don't think I've ever seen such
a big one before! You made it, <PARENT>?
I bet it could make the town famous!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Whoa! Amazing! You're a farming master,
<PARENT>! I've never seen a watermelon
this big before!
<PAGE>
Do you think eating this much watermelon
will make me fat? Nah, I should  be
fine! Surely!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Wow! I don't think I've ever seen such
a big one before! However did you grow
it?
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>I'll take it, but how am I going to eat
it?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Thank you, <PARENT>. But I don't need this
right now.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I can't carry that much! Maybe next
time?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present for me? Wow! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
<PARENT>'s pancakes! Wow, these taste
great!
<PAGE>
Can you teach me how to make these? Then
I can make them for you.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present for me? Wow! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
Thank you, <PARENT>! Wow, this looks
delicious!
<PAGE>
Tastes great! Birthdays are fun, aren't
they?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present for me? Wow! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
Great! My  present from you, <PARENT>!
I'm going to show this to everyone.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present for me? Wow! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
Thank you, <PARENT>! I'm so happy!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present for me? Wow! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>Hold on, <PARENT>. You know I hate this,
right? Are you kidding? Where's my real
present?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present for me? Wow! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>How could you give me this on my
birthday? Haven't I been a good
daughter? I-I hate you, <PARENT>!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present for me? Wow! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
I still can't eat grilled pumpkin, even
though I'm grown up. Give me something
else!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
What? A birthday present for me? Wow!
Great! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
It's a big watermelon! Wow, thanks
<PARENT>! I'll eat as much of it as I can!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
What? A birthday present for me? Wow!
Great! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
Wow! I don't think I've ever seen such
a big one before! Thanks! I'll cook
something with it later.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present? For me? Yay! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
Wow! A giant watermelon! I appreciate
this a lot, but if I can't eat it all,
can you help me finish it, <PARENT>?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A birthday present for me? Wow! Thank
you! What did you get me?
<PAGE>
Wow! I don't think I've ever seen such
a big one before! I bet I can make all
sorts of things with this.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Chicks look even smaller now that I've
gotten bigger.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Chickens were so hard to catch when I
was small, but it's easy for me now.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I remember wanting to make this big
chicken my bodyguard, but now I'm far
bigger.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Does our dog still recognize me? Yes,
look! Wow, that's great!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
So heavy... what have you been feeding
our dog? How about some exercise?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I remember riding our dog around...
I'll do it again, once I return to
being  small.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
You're too fat! I'm going to walk you
from now on, so come on mutt, on your
paws! What? No response!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Our cat sometimes comes into my bed and
curls up on top of me. It always wakes
me up.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
How soft and fluffy! I can't get enough
of this cutie's plush fur!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Our cat only comes near me when I'm
eating. Then it just saunters off again.
What a funny animal!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Ugh, so heavy... I'm bigger now, too,
but I still can't lift our cat.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Thank you, <PARENT>. What a lovely present
for a lovely day!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
A Pumpkin Festival present! Wow, thanks!
<PAGE>
I love the treats you make, <PARENT>! They
always taste so good.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
You use a Blue Feather when you're grown
up, right? So can I use one now?
<PAGE>
No? Why not? Why won't you tell me?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Can I try this ring on? Wow, it's a
perfect fit!
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>Hey, <PARENT>. Can I have this ring? What?
I can't?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I wonder if they'd like some bread
crumbs... look, they're eating them! How
cute!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
They're so friendly. It's because you're
looking after them, <PARENT>.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Turtle shells are so hard. They look
like a rock when the legs and head are
inside.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>. Close your eyes and put out your
hands. Come on, play along!
<PAGE>
Now you can open them. It's your
birthday present from me! I hope you
like it.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I'm sorry, <PARENT>. I wasn't able to get
a birthday present for you...

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<PARENT>... are you going to stop talking
to me now that I'm bigger? Come on,
let's talk more!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Yay! It's the ocean! Hey, can I go
swimming by myself?
<PAGE>
Now that I'm grown up, I want to try
going out there alone!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Is that turtle over there the same
turtle that we always see in that spot?
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>Now that I'm bigger, a lot of things
look smaller than they used to!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>! I want one of those coconuts
from that palm tree there!
<PAGE>
I can't climb up and get it! That's no
way for a young lady to act.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Now that I'm bigger, I'm not afraid of
ghosts anymore!
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>W-Well I guess I'm a little scared. 
N-No, I mean, I'm not scared... I'm not
scared at all.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
The mask on the wall there is actually
quite interesting, when you look at it
closely.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
You know, I climbed to the very top of
those stairs!
<PAGE>
It was really high, and I could see
mountains that are super far away!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Ahaha! I can reach the branches of the
cherry trees now!
<PAGE>
Check it out, <PARENT>! Aren't I amazing!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Hey, <PARENT>! If you're going to go
fishing, can I come with you?
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>You always look like you're having so
much fun when you're fishing. I want to
try too. It's okay, right?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Lah lah lah... Lah laaah... Lah lah lah
laah laaah!
<PAGE>
So many things look different when you
get bigger, don't they. I want to see
as much as I can!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Alright! I'm going to make a big
snowman!
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>You just watch, <PARENT>! I can do it all
by myself now.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>, let's have a snowball fight.
Take this!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Ah, ah, ahchoo! Uhhh.
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>It-It's nothing! I'm just fine! Okay?
<PAGE>
<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>Come on! Let's keep playing!

<PARENT>... Don't worry... I'm an adult
now... I won't wet the bed anymore.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
My body feels sluggish. Maybe I caught a
cold.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Hey, <PARENT>. Do you want some help
tomorrow?

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Oh. That's too bad. Maybe next time
then.

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Great! You can count on me to work hard!

<FACE_DAUGHTER><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
The food today is so delicious. I
feel so happy right now... so blessed.
Now's not the time to give a present.
